Naina - AI Therapy Assistant

🌟 Overview

Naina is an AI-powered therapy assistant designed to provide empathetic and intelligent mental health support. Built using GPT-3.5 Turbo, Naina offers personalized conversations, emotional guidance, and therapeutic exercises to help users navigate mental well-being challenges.

🚀 Features

Conversational AI: Engages users with meaningful and empathetic discussions.

Therapy Guidance: Provides mental health tips and coping strategies.

Personalized Responses: Understands context and tailors replies to user needs.

Secure & Private: Ensures user data confidentiality and safety.

Web Deployment: Hosted with Flask for easy accessibility.


🔧 Tech Stack

Backend: Python, Flask

AI Model: GPT-3.5 Turbo (via OpenAI API)

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

Deployment: Google Colab (for initial testing), Flask (for web integration)


📂 Installation

1️⃣ Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/your-username/Naina.git
cd Naina

2️⃣ Install Dependencies

pip install -r requirements.txt

3️⃣ Set Up OpenAI API Key

Create a .env file and add your OpenAI API key:

OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

4️⃣ Run the Application

python app.py

🛠 Future Enhancements

Integrating voice-based interactions.

Emotion detection for more personalized therapy sessions.

Mobile app version for better accessibility.
